PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (SALT RIVER FIRST NATION, N.W.T.) - which provides for the withdrawal from disposal, until August 31, 2006, of some 41,942 hectares of land, near Fort Smith, in order to facilitate the settlement of land claims made by the Salt River First Nation.
